targets.query:
trackerData = from(bucket: "rockoon")
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_measurement"] == "tracker")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_field"] == "latitude" or r["_field"] == "longitude")
  |> pivot(rowKey:["_time"], columnKey: ["_field"], valueColumn: "_value")
  |> map(fn: (r) => ({
      r with
      tracker_latitude: float(v: r.latitude) / 10000.0,
      tracker_longitude: float(v: r.longitude) / 10000.0
    }))

missionData = from(bucket: "rockoon")
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_measurement"] == "mission")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_field"] == "latitude" or r["_field"] == "longitude")
  |> pivot(rowKey:["_time"], columnKey: ["_field"], valueColumn: "_value")
  |> map(fn: (r) => ({
      r with
      mission_latitude: float(v: r.latitude) / 10000.0,
      mission_longitude: float(v: r.longitude) / 10000.0
    }))

union(tables: [trackerData, missionData])
  |> yield(name: "result")

from(bucket: "rockoon")
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_measurement"] == "tracker")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_field"] == "latitude")
  |> aggregateWindow(every: v.windowPeriod, fn: mean, createEmpty: false)
  |> map(fn: (r) => ({r with _value: r._value / 10000.0}))
  |> yield(name: "mean")

from(bucket: "rockoon")
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_measurement"] == "tracker")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_field"] == "latitude")
  |> aggregateWindow(every: v.windowPeriod, fn: mean, createEmpty: false)
  |> map(fn: (r) => ({
      
      deg: int(v: r._value / 10000.0),  
      min: int(v: ((r._value / 10000.0) - float(v: int(v: r._value / 10000.0))) * 60.0),  // Extract minutes
      sec: ((((r._value / 10000.0) - float(v: int(v: r._value / 10000.0)))) * 60.0 % 1.0) * 60.0
    }))
  |> yield(name: "mean")
